    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよ今日から、写真集の撮影開始やね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So the photo shoot for the photo book starts today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "京都は優の地元だし、張り切っているみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem pumped since we're in your hometown of Kyoto‚ Yu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.0955781619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.0204081853
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです。しかも最初の撮影場所が鴨川なんて\nスタッフさんもよう分かってはるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. And the first location is Kamogawa?\nThe staff really know what they're doing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.9696598054
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "今回の写真集のコンセプトは、読者がうちと\nデートしてる気分を味わえることやからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The concept for this photo book is for the readers\nTo feel like they're on a date with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.6652817465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "鴨川は有名なデートスポットやし\nコンセプトにぴったりや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The Kamogawa River is a famous date spot‚\nSo it's a perfect fit for the concept.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.1163266661
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに周りはカップルだらけだな\n俺達だけ浮いてる気がするよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's true that we're surrounded by couples.\nI feel like we're the only ones who stand out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.8296597324
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "浮いてる？　それはあきません。うちらも周りに\n負けないくらいラブラブな雰囲気を作らな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We stand out? We can’t have that. We need to\nCreate a lovey-dovey vibe that can compete with everyone else.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんでそうなるんだ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-why does it have to be like that…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.1417002839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.6573464713
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "写真集を買う人は、うちとカップルになって\nラブラブなデートをする気分を味わいたいんや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The people buying the photo book want to feel like\nThey’re on a lovey-dovey date with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "そのためには、ラブラブな雰囲気を\n写真で表現する必要があるやろ？　だから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And to do that‚ we need to express that lovey-dovey vibe\nIn the photos‚ right? So…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.1073435391,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.5669833503
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんはうちの恋人役になって\nラブラブな雰囲気作りに協力してもらいます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san will be playing the role of my boyfriend‚\nAnd help me create a lovey-dovey mood!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.2085707031
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、雰囲気作りなら一人でも出来るだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ you can do that alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.2085707031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\nうちはふざけて言ってるんとちゃいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nI’m not joking.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.0783439639
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "最高の仕事をするには、事前の準備が大事や\nこの間のライブバトルで、うちはそれを学びました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To do the best job‚ preparation is key.\nI learned that from our last live battle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "ファンの期待に応えるためにも、やるからには本気で\nラブラブなデートの雰囲気を再現せなあかんのです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To meet our fans' expectations‚ we need to seriously\nRecreate the vibe of a lovey-dovey date!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.4562189616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kamogawa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kamogawa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.495713584
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、二人でいちゃいちゃしながら散歩しよか\nなんなら恋人らしく腕を組んでもええよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So with that said‚ let’s take a walk while acting all lovey-dovey.\nIf you want‚ you can even hold my arm like a real couple?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "優……俺をからかって楽しんでるだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu… you’re enjoying teasing me‚ aren’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.6468242649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.9203842327
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.9203842327
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "次は、デート中にお茶屋さんで\n休憩してるシチュエーションやね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Next is a situation where we’re taking a break at a teahouse\nDuring a date.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.9670507276
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "……という訳で、{user}さん\nまたラブラブな雰囲気作りに協力してくれへん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So with that said‚ {user}-san‚\nWill you help me create that lovey-dovey vibe again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "今度は何をさせる気だ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you going to make me do this time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.8123111888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.2290459159
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "そんな警戒せんでええよ。ちょっとこのお団子を\nうちにあーんして食べさせてくれればいいだけやから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No need to be so guarded. You just need to\nFeed this dango to me saying “ahh”.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、周りの目もあるんだし\nさすがにそれは勘弁してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way‚ with everyone watching…\nI’ll have to pass on that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.2628160559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.5956439181
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "恥ずかしがらずに、ちゃんと食べさせてくれな困るわ\nこれもマネージャーの仕事ですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t be shy‚ I’ll be troubled if you don’t feed me properly.\nThis is also part of your job as manager‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、それはマネージャーの仕事じゃないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ that's not part of a manager's job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.5074353381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.0919930939
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_08_02-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "意固地やなぁ……\n分かりました。ほな、食べさせてもらうのは諦めます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're so stubborn…\nAlright. Then I’ll give up on being fed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
